text: Kochanów () is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Kamienna Góra, within Kamienna Góra County, Lower Silesian Voivodeship, in south- western Poland. Prior to 1945 it was in Germany. It lies approximately south- east of Kamienna Góra, and south-west of the regional capital Wrocław.
